commit.message: Updated network params file with new keys.

Add Gibbs sampling and refactored edge selection code

Gibbs sampling can be enabled by adding "edgeSelectionAlgorithm GibbsSampling" to the network parameters file.

Currently logging is enabled only when the sampling method is "ExactRandom" (default)
